        <head>Robin</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>If I can stop one heart from breaking,</l>
          <l>I shall not live in vain;</l>
          <l>If I can ease one life the aching,</l>
          <l>Or cool one pain,</l>
          <l>Or help one fainting robin</l>
          <l>Unto his nest again,</l>
          <l>I shall not live in vain.</l>
        </lg>
